   "source": "# Lesson 15 \u2014 outlines"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "**E1.** From $x_1 + x_2 \\le 5$: $x_1 \\le 5 - 0 = 5$, $x_2 \\le 5$. From $2 x_1 - x_2 \\ge 1$: $x_1 \\ge (1 + 0)/2 = 0.5$. Iterate: bounds become $x_1 \\in [0.5, 5], x_2 \\in [0, 5]$ (no further tightening)."
  }
